title: The Durham Late Show Roast Session w/ DC Young Fly, Karlous Miller and Chico BEan | Ep. 193
itunes:title: The Durham Late Show Roast Session w/ DC Young Fly, Karlous Miller and Chico BEan | Ep. 193
description:
On this classic episode, Durham brought everybody out to The Carolina Theater for the laughs. At this wild show, one lady snuck her new born baby in the show, Chico stole a wheelchair, and a 13 year old and his momma get roasted from the balcony all night long. Plus, Karlous Miller, DC Young Fly and Chico Bean come up with an all-new TV show idea - Three Baby Daddies on The Couch! You gotta watch DC Young Fly doing his sex blow up doll impersonation! This is the coldest podcast!
